entries.precis: Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the evening. The chance of an evening thunderstorm, possibly severe. Winds northerly 15 to 25 km/h.

Slight (20%) chance of a shower or thunderstorm in the early morning. Sunny day. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h turning west to southwesterly before dawn then tending west to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h in the middle of the day.
Sunny. Light winds becoming northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h early in the morning then tending westerly 20 to 30 km/h in the morning.
Partly cloudy. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning then becoming light during the evening.
Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower in the afternoon and evening. Light winds becoming northerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning then tending northwesterly 25 to 35 km/h during the day.
Partly cloudy. Winds northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h tending westerly 25 to 35 km/h during the morning.
Sunny. Winds west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h turning south to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Light winds becoming easterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
